data.description: A Rare Find! Large Duplex With 1300 Sq Ft Per Side, And 2 Car Garage! Excellent Investment Opportunity, Or Finance Your Homestead! Updates Include:Gorgeous, New 12x24 Tile Throughout, AC Units New 2018, New Pump, Brand New Water System (Right Side), Plus New Softener (Left Side),New Vanities In Both Masters, Freshly Painted Inside And Out! New Outside Lighting And All Cement Driveway. Also Boasts Large, Separate Dining Rooms, Kitchen Pantries, And Walk In Closets In Master. Fantastic Private Location On Low Traffic, Dead End Street. Quick Access To RSW Airport, I-75, Jet Blue Park-Red Sox Training, Hammond Stadium, And FGCU. Nearby To Shopping And Restaurants At Gulf Coast Town Center, Miromar Outlets, And Fabulous Beaches. This Is A One Of A Kind And Will Not Last--Set Your Showing Today--Priced To Sell!
